title: 099: Adam's Road to the San Jose Pro: Week 3 Update
description: Adam just has a little more than a week to go before appearing on the San Jose Pro stage. In this episode he details his diet, workouts and challenges as he builds his best physique ever. The date of the San Jose Pro is the evening of June 27th. If you are in the area, join MindPump and Adam's fans to cheer him on! It is being held at the Santa Clara Convention Center, 5001 Great America Pkwy, Santa Clara, CA 95054
